data.description: This beautiful Zen inspired, open-concept home features 4 beds, 2 baths & garage or bonus space. Step inside and you'll be greeted by a bright, open living space leading to the stunning, renovated Chef's kitchen with new stainless appliances, 2 sinks and a massive white and gray marbled granite island leaving plenty of space for entertaining! Perfect floorplan features Primary Bedroom with attached bathroom and double vanities with upgraded walk-in shower. Upgraded French doors lead you outside to a covered patio, large grass area big enough for pool, fire pit, &  shed. New A/C motor, no HOA, all exterior windows resealed, along with award-winning Chandler schools and million dollar updated park just steps away. Dream big and make this your home today!
